<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6830b255bd0a13a55b556d6e2863dda35f167a","tid":525811,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"初中段好睇 但之後爛尾"},{"pid":"fd5f8663735e3df8a45f204ab0d5b57addd75206","tid":525811,"uid":48680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"呢套係<br />\n心理學(順便鬥智)漫畫<br />\n<br />\n點解呢套漫畫正<br />\n係因為佢唔過份賣弄小聰明 <br />\n而係探討人性/心理衝突(雖然深度不足)<br />\n我真心認為呢套係後半 好過前半<br />\n<br />\n外傳更加好多都屈機<br />\n九頭龍/魔女/King/Q 呢系列既game<br />\n先係作者真正想寫既心理遊戲<br />\n<br />\n雖然你只係鐘意鬥智遊戲既話<br />\n就只有前半部份了<br />\n<br />\nps: 捉依因 的確係一大敗筆<br />\n太突兀了"},{"pid":"559bced43842e2e0054100ab23c7a1aee91d0f1d","tid":525811,"uid":50242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:25:37.000Z","msg":"我反而鍾意一開始四卡車三卡毒氣紅心二<br />\n夠簡單夠絕望"},{"pid":"bca3aed1b17ec0d787e911059f2622a73720519d","tid":525811,"uid":48680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T20:17:26.000Z","msg":"唔算純死亡遊戲類<br />\n但我諗 死囚樂園 deadman wonderland<br />\n<br />\n應該會係樓主杯茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9c471cc0ebf6aa1a010be0cbced1e279adb983","tid":525811,"uid":164583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T20:31:25.000Z","msg":"噬謊者，<br />\n睇一次你就明個遊戲我話你叻"},{"pid":"42c6af494f01bbe16d651327303548f549eba10c","tid":525811,"uid":46488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T00:33:28.000Z","msg":"無見過呢類題材既漫畫可以有彌留一樣既結局<br />\n話結局差既人個腦係咪裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f73ac28de661640df602e4952a045143b479539","tid":525811,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T00:42:48.000Z","msg":"個人覺得開頭公寓果個好正，有一次睇漫畫睇得到咁緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc97a535ec1ff5be4cec10bf6275f45642ed3f6b","tid":525811,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike